There, you can open issues about new functionalies, bugs or another questions. Also, you
can improve source code and send it via pull request.
</p>
<h2>5) How can you add support to other language?</h2>
<BR />
<p>
    The key are in <a href="https://github.com/dafuer/GetOptGenerator/tree/master/src/Dafuer/GetOptGeneratorBundle/Entity/Generator" target="blank">generator folder</a>. 
    You must modify Generator class in order to add your language to languajes array. Then, you
    must create LanguageGenerator class extending Generator class and it must implement
    defined abstract method. You can use other generator like examples. At last, if you 
    have troubles, make questions via GitHub. Good luck!
</p>
